NK063(gu)002:1: // chos tshoms ngos gzung ba zhes bya ba bzhugs so //
NK063(gu)002:3: bla ma rnams la rab btud rgyud rgyal gyi //
NK063(gu)002:4: le don re la'ang dbang po'i bye brag gis //
NK063(gu)002:5: chos mtshan gsum las gang ston ngos gzung zhing //
NK063(gu)002:6: gang gi yul yin rnam bzhir bsdus 'di nyon //
NK063(gu)002:7: 'dir chos tshoms ngos gzung ba zhes bya ba le'u re re nas kyang /
NK063(gu)002:8: dbang po rab kyi chos gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum las gang ston pa dang /
NK063(gu)002:10: btags pa'i gzhi gnyis las gang ston /
NK063(gu)002:11: lam la thun mong dang thun mong min pa gnyis las gang ston /
NK063(gu)002:12: thun mong min pa la thabs grol gnyis las gang ston /
NK063(gu)002:13: thabs lam la steng sgo 'og sgo gnyis las gang /
NK063(gu)002:14: grol lam la rim gyis pa dang cig car gnyis las gang /
NK063(gu)002:15: 'bras bu la gnas skabs dang mthar thug gi las gang /
NK063(gu)002:16: mthar thug la bdag don grub pa po dang gzhan
NK063(gu)002:17: don mdzad pa po las gang ston zhes ngos gzung
NK063(gu)002:24: gleng gzhi la thun mong gi dang thun min gnyis las gang /
NK063(gu)002:25: thun mong la rgyud 'byung ba khyad par can dang /
NK063(gu)002:26: bstan pa 'byung ba spyi gnyis las gang zhes pa dang /
NK063(gu)002:27: rgyud don la bcu las gang /
NK063(gu)002:28: de'i bye brag dkyil 'khor bdun las gang zhes ngos gzung ngo //
NK063(gu)002:29: dbang po tha ma'i chos mtshon byed kyi bshad thabs bcu las /
NK063(gu)002:30: spyir 'gro ba gsum gyi steng du khyad par ba gang gis ston zhes ngos gzung zhing /
NK063(gu)002:31: de ltar ston pa'i le'u de gang zag dang lam
NK063(gu)002:32: pa gang gi yul yin pa dang bzhir ngos gzung
NK063(gu)002:33: bar bya'o // de la brtsad cha na re /
NK063(gu)002:36: tha ma rnams la ngos gzung bar mi 'thad de /
NK063(gu)002:39: gdams gtad rnams yin pa'i phyir ro zer yang /
NK063(gu)002:40: de dag la 'bring gi chos rgyud don ngos gzung bar mi 'thad pa yin gyi /
NK063(gu)002:41: gzhan rnams ngos gzung bar 'thad pa'i phyir //
NK063(gu)002:42: dang po gleng gzhi'i le'u la /
NK063(gu)002:44: le'u'i ngo bo ni dag pa de pa'i snang ba 'bras bu'i rgyud yin no //
NK063(gu)002:45: mtshan dang gleng gzhi mdor bstan gnyis lam dang sbyar
NK063(gu)002:46: nas 'chad pa'i phyir khyad par gyi lam thabs grol
NK063(gu)002:48: thabs lam steng 'og gi sgo gnyis char ston no //
NK063(gu)002:49: 'bring gi chos lnga las gleng gazhi'o //
NK063(gu)002:51: de las rgyud 'byung ba khyad par can gyi'o //
NK063(gu)002:52: tha ma'i chos bcu las khyab byed gsum gyi steng
NK063(gu)002:53: du de bzhin nyid kyi dbyings zhes pas rang bzhin
NK063(gu)002:55: le'u bsdu ba yod pas spyi don sdud pa dang /
NK063(gu)002:56: mtshan dang gleng gzhi mdor bstan 'og sgor 'chad pas ldem dgongs man ngag dang /
NK063(gu)002:57: de la rtsod spong yod pas gtar kha gegs sel dang /
NK063(gu)002:58: thal rgyud rgya mtsho la sogs lung du ma drangs pas tshad ma bka' gzhung dang /
NK063(gu)002:59: dper na til gyi gang bu zhes pas mtshon pa dpe'i tshig dang /
NK063(gu)002:60: ston pa'i ngo bo 'og nas len pas bsnol mtshams 'phen sdud de /
NK063(gu)002:61: de ltar khyad par bdun dang bcu khas ston no //
NK063(gu)002:62: 'di ni mthar phyin de pa'i yul lo //
NK063(gu)002:63: gnyis pa gleng slang ba'i le'u la /
NK063(gu)002:64: rab kyi chos la gsum las /
NK063(gu)002:65: le'u ngo bo 'bras bu yin cing /
NK063(gu)002:66: bcing med rnam par grol med pa //
NK063(gu)002:67: ye nas lhun grub ces pas ngo bo'i gzhi dang /
NK063(gu)002:68: rang gi rnam rtog las kyis sprul //
NK063(gu)002:69: la sogs pas btags pa'i gzhi gnyis ka ston no //
NK063(gu)002:70: lam las khyad par gyi lam thabs grol gnyis ka
NK063(gu)002:71: ston te sems bskyed pa'i skabs su thabs lam 'og
NK063(gu)002:72: sgo dang / grol lam cig car ba'o //
NK063(gu)002:73: 'bring gi lnga las gleng slang ba'o //
NK063(gu)002:74: de la'ang thun min thun mong gnyis ka'o //
NK063(gu)002:76: lta ba dang ldem dgongs tshad ma bka' gzhung rnams
NK063(gu)002:77: shas ches gtar kha dang bsnol mtshams zur tsam mo
NK063(gu)002:78: // 'dir thun mong gi gleng slang yod pas kun gyi yul lo //
NK063(gu)002:79: gsum pa chos thams cad gtan la phab pa'i le'u la /
NK063(gu)002:81: rang bzhin nyid las nyams pa med //
NK063(gu)002:82: ces pas ngo bo'i gzhi dang /
NK063(gu)002:83: ji snyed lo ka 'khrul pa'i chos //
NK063(gu)002:84: la sogs pas btags pa'i gzhi gnyis ka ston /
NK063(gu)002:85: lam las thun mong gi lam dang /
NK063(gu)002:86: khyad par gyi lam gnyis ston /
NK063(gu)002:87: de las grol lam rim gyis pa /
NK063(gu)002:88: de las kyang rgyu shes pa gtan tshigs kyis lta ba gtan la phab pa ston /
NK063(gu)002:89: 'bras bu la thub pa'i sku gsung thugs bsam gyis mi khyab pas gzhan don mdzad pa po ston /
NK063(gu)002:90: 'bring gi chos lnga las stod nas bstan pa 'byung ba spyi'i gleng gzhi ston la /
NK063(gu)002:91: smad nas nyer gcig pa yan chad du yongs su
NK063(gu)002:92: shes par bya ba'i dngos po rgyud dngos ston par
NK063(gu)002:93: kun 'dra la / de la lam gyi ngo bo dang /
NK063(gu)002:95: ngo bo ni rab kyi chos kyi skabs su ngos 'dzin pa'ang kun mthun no //
NK063(gu)002:96: cha rkyen gyi bcu las 'di nas lta ba ston /
NK063(gu)002:97: de las gzhal bya gtan tshigs grub mtha' gsum ston /
NK063(gu)002:99: khyad par ba rang bzhin lta ba spyi don sdud pa /
NK063(gu)002:101: gtar kha gegs sel rnams shas che /
NK063(gu)002:105: bzhi pa yi ge phreng ba 'khor lo bkod pa'i le'u la rab kyi gsum las /
NK063(gu)002:106: a ni stong dang mi stong gi //
NK063(gu)002:107: la sogs pa bden pa bzhi dbyer med du gtan la 'bebs pas ngo bo'i gazhi'o //
NK063(gu)002:108: lam las khyad par gyi lam grol lam cig car ba zur tsam la /
NK063(gu)002:109: rim gyis pa shas che bar ston /
NK063(gu)002:110: bsdu ba'i skabs su thabs lam 'og sgo zur tsam mo //
NK063(gu)002:111: yi ge sku gsum gyi ngo bor sangs rgyas pa ston pas 'bras bu zur tsam mo //
NK063(gu)002:112: 'bring gi rgyun don la yang gnyis las /
NK063(gu)002:113: cha rkye ni lta ba dang /
NK063(gu)002:114: dkyil 'khor las sa ma ti'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK063(gu)002:116: ting nge 'dzin las bskyed pa'i ting nge 'dzin ston /
NK063(gu)002:117: sngags dang phyag rgya las sngags kyi ngo bo +aa li k+aa li'o //
NK063(gu)002:118: des yi ge'i sgo nas tshogs sgrub pa ston /
NK063(gu)002:120: rang bzhin lta ba ldem dgongs gtar kha rnams zur tsam dang /
NK063(gu)002:121: tshad ma bka' gzhung dang bsnol mtshams 'phen sdud shas cher ston /
NK063(gu)002:122: 'di dngos su phyag rgya gcig pa phra mo'i yul la /
NK063(gu)002:123: shugs la zag bcas kyi lam kun gyi yul lo //
NK063(gu)002:124: lnga pa sgyu 'phrul bsgrub pa ting nge 'dzin gyi le'u la /
NK063(gu)002:125: rab kyi chos la gsum char te gzhi las /
NK063(gu)002:126: gzhi rtsa med pa'i sems nyid ni //
NK063(gu)002:127: la sogs pa ngo bo'i gzhi ston /
NK063(gu)002:128: lam las thun mong gi dngos grub rnams khyad par gyi lam thabs grol gnyis kar 'chad cing /
NK063(gu)002:129: thabs lam steng 'og gnyis ka ston la /
NK063(gu)002:130: grol lam cig car ba zur tsam dang /
NK063(gu)002:131: rim gyis pa shas che bar ston //
NK063(gu)002:132: 'bras bu las mthar thug gi 'bras bu bdag don grub pa dang /
NK063(gu)002:133: gzhan don mdzad pa gnyis ka ston /
NK063(gu)002:134: 'bring gi cha rkyen las lta ba dang /
NK063(gu)002:139: gtso bor sgrub pa ston pa'i phyir gzhan rnams kun shugs la ston pa yin no //
NK063(gu)002:140: tha ma'i rang bzhin lta ba ldem dgongs gtar kha bsnol mtshams tshad ma bka' gzhung mtshon pa dape'o //
NK063(gu)002:142: drug pa sku'i dkyil 'khor bstan pa'i le'u la /
NK063(gu)002:145: rdzogs chen rtogs pa'i rnal 'byor pas //
NK063(gu)002:148: lam las thun mong gi lam ston /
NK063(gu)002:149: khyad par gyi lam las grol lam rim gyis pa shas che /
NK063(gu)002:150: ngo bo'i gzhi ston pa'i phyir cig car ba zur tsam mo //
NK063(gu)002:152: de las thun mong pa dang khyad par gyi lam
NK063(gu)002:153: gnyis ka nas grub pa bdag don grub pa po
NK063(gu)002:154: yin la / shugs la gzhan don mdzad pa yang ston /
NK063(gu)002:156: rdzogs chen rtogs pa'i zhes pas lta ba dang /
NK063(gu)002:158: ces pas gcig car ba blang dor med pa'i spyod pa dang /
NK063(gu)002:159: tsakra rtsi bas bzhi zhes pa la sogs zhi ba lhag pa sa ma ti sku'i dang /
NK063(gu)002:160: rang bzhin mthar phyin dkyil 'khor rnams so //
NK063(gu)002:161: tha ma'i rang bzhin lta ba tshad ma mtshon pa'i
NK063(gu)002:162: dpe bsnol mtshams gtar ga spyi don sdud pa rnams
NK063(gu)002:163: / 'di ni phyag rgya spros bcas kyi'o //
NK063(gu)002:164: bdun pa gsung gi dkyil 'khor gyi le'u la /
NK063(gu)002:165: rab kyi lam dang 'bras bu ste /
NK063(gu)002:166: lam las khyad par ba grol lam rim gyis pa dang /
NK063(gu)002:167: sngags rnams thabs lam 'og sgo cung zad ston /
NK063(gu)002:168: 'bras bu las rang bzhin ni 'bras bu mthar phyin pa gsung gi dkyil 'khor ro //
NK063(gu)002:169: 'bring gi cha rkyen la dkyil 'khor las /
NK063(gu)002:170: zhi ba lhag pa gsung gi dang /
NK063(gu)002:171: sa ma ti las bskyed rim dang /
NK063(gu)002:172: sngags dang phyag rgya rnams so //
NK063(gu)002:173: tha ma'i khyad par ba rang bzhin lta ba dang /
NK063(gu)002:174: spyi don sdud pa ma yin pa lngas ston pa las /
NK063(gu)002:176: 'di ni stod spros bcas la smad mthar lam gyi yul lo //
NK063(gu)002:177: brgyad pa thugs kyi dkyil 'khor gyi le'u la /
NK063(gu)002:178: rab kyi gsum las rang bzhin dang lta ba phyag rgya ston pas gzhi zur tsam mo //
NK063(gu)002:179: lam las khyad par ba grol lam rim gyis pa shas che /
NK063(gu)002:180: gsang dbang sbyin pa'i skabs su thabs lam 'og sgo zur tsam mo //
NK063(gu)002:182: so sor mthun byas kun tu ston //
NK063(gu)002:184: gzhan don mdzad pa por mi 'gal lo //
NK063(gu)002:185: 'bring gi cha rkyen lta ba dang /
NK063(gu)002:186: spyod pa las spros bcas kyi dang /
NK063(gu)002:187: dkyil 'khor las lhag pa sa ma ti thugs kyi dang /
NK063(gu)002:188: dbang las gsang dbang zur tsam dang /
NK063(gu)002:189: sa ma ti las bskyed rim gyi dang /
NK063(gu)002:190: p+au dza las phyag rgya'i dang /
NK063(gu)002:191: sngags dang phyag rgya las phyag rgya 'da' daka'o zhes pas /
NK063(gu)002:192: dam tshig kyang shugs la ston pas mi 'gal lo //
NK063(gu)002:193: tha ma'i khyad par ba spyi don sdud pa ma yin pa drug gis so //
NK063(gu)002:195: dgu pa lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor gyi le'u la /
NK063(gu)002:196: rab kyi gsum char te gzhi las ngo bo'i gzhi zur tsam dang /
NK063(gu)002:197: lam las khyad par ba thabs grol gnyis car ro //
NK063(gu)002:199: grol lam rim gyis pa shas che /
NK063(gu)002:201: 'bras bu las gnas skabs kyi rig 'dzin bzhi char /
NK063(gu)002:202: mthar thug gi grub mdzad gnyis char ro //
NK063(gu)002:203: 'bring gi cha rkyen las dngos su dkyil 'khor dang /
NK063(gu)002:204: dbang dang sgrub pa gsum ston la /
NK063(gu)002:205: shugs la bcu char ston no //
NK063(gu)002:206: tha ma'i khyad par ba bdun ka 'jug pas bcu char gyis 'chad /
NK063(gu)002:208: bcu pa dbang bskur ba'i le'u la /
NK063(gu)002:209: rab kyi gtso bor lam dang 'bras bu zur tsam mo //
NK063(gu)002:210: lam las khyad par ba thabs lam 'og sgo kho na'o //
NK063(gu)002:211: nyan dbang ni grol lam rim gyis par cung zad gzung /
NK063(gu)002:212: 'bring gi cha rkyen dbang kho nas te /
NK063(gu)002:213: de'i cha rkyen du dgu char shugs la gnas pa'i phyir ston no //
NK063(gu)002:214: tha ma'i khyad par ba ldem dgongs dang /
NK063(gu)002:215: tshad ma bka' gzhung gtar ga rnams gtso che /
NK063(gu)002:216: gzhan bzhis kyang shugs la zur tsam 'chad do //
NK063(gu)002:217: 'di yang zag bcas nas mthar lam gyi bar dbang bskur ba'i phyir /
NK063(gu)002:219: bcu gcig pa tshogs kyi le'u dang /
NK063(gu)002:220: bcu gnyis pa sgrub pa'i le'u la /
NK063(gu)002:222: gzhi las gtan tshigs gtan la dbab pa btags gzhi dang ngo bo'i gzhi gnyis char ro //
NK063(gu)002:223: lam las khyad par ba thabs bral gnyis char ro //
NK063(gu)002:225: grol lam rim gyis pa dang cig car pa gnyis ka ston /
NK063(gu)002:226: 'bras bu las gnas skabs kyi rig 'dzin bzhi char
NK063(gu)002:227: dang mthar thug gi bdag don grub pa dang gzhan
NK063(gu)002:228: don mdzad pa gnyis char ro //
NK063(gu)002:229: 'bring gi cha rkyen dgos su tshogs sgrub kho na ste /
NK063(gu)002:230: de'i cha rkyen du bcu char ston no //
NK063(gu)002:231: tha ma'i khyad par ba bdun dang bcu char gyis 'chad /
NK063(gu)002:232: 'di ni le'u'i ngo bo tshogs sgrub pa yin la /
NK063(gu)002:233: 'di nas rgyu shes pa lta ba gtan la dbab
NK063(gu)002:234: pa nas mthar phyin 'bras bu'i bar du ma lus
NK063(gu)002:235: par ston pas kun gyi yul lo //
NK063(gu)002:236: bcu gsum pa shin tu gsal ba man ngag gi le'u la /
NK063(gu)002:237: rab kyi gsum char te gzhi las btags pa'i dang /
NK063(gu)002:238: ngo bo'i gzhi gnyis char ro //
NK063(gu)002:239: lam las le'u stod thun mong gi lam la smad khyad par gyi lam ste /
NK063(gu)002:240: de yang stod grol lam rim gyis pa yin la smad grol lam cig car ba dang /
NK063(gu)002:241: thabs lam steng 'og gi sgo gnyis char ro //
NK063(gu)002:242: 'bras bu la gong ltar gnas skabs kyi bzhi char dang mthar thug gi gnyis char ro //
NK063(gu)002:243: 'bring gi cha rkyen ni phyi nang gi theg pa thams cad kyi lta ba dang /
NK063(gu)002:244: dkyil 'khor las lhag pa'i ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK063(gu)002:247: tha ma'i bcu char gyis so //
NK063(gu)002:249: bcu bzhi pa bstod pa'i le'u la /
NK063(gu)002:250: rab kyi chos le'u'i ngo bo mthar thug gi 'bras bu'o //
NK063(gu)002:251: 'bring gi cha rkyen mchod par ngos cung zad bzung /
NK063(gu)002:252: tha ma'i mtshon pa dpe dang /
NK063(gu)002:254: 'di bstod bya rgyal ba yin la /
NK063(gu)002:255: stod byed 'di ltar gang gis bstod kyang rung ste kun gyi yul lo //
NK063(gu)002:256: bco lnga pa khro bo rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor rnam par spros pa'i le'u la /
NK063(gu)002:257: rab kyi gsum char te gzhi las ngo bo'i dang gol gzhi'i gnyis ka'o //
NK063(gu)002:258: lam las khyad par ba thabs grol gnyis char ro //
NK063(gu)002:259: de yang thabs lam ni sngon byung gi zab mo'i dbang yin la /
NK063(gu)002:260: bskyed rim ni grol lam rim gyis pa'o //
NK063(gu)002:261: 'bras bu lam mthar thug gi gzhan don mdzad pa'o //
NK063(gu)002:262: 'bring gi cha rkyen ni lta ba dang /
NK063(gu)002:263: thabs lam brtul zhugs kyi spyod pa dang /
NK063(gu)002:264: dkyil 'khor las khro bo lhag pa ting nge 'dzin sku'i dkyil 'khor ro //
NK063(gu)002:265: dbang las zab mo'i dbang sngon byung gi'o //
NK063(gu)002:266: dam tshig gi ni nyams pa'i rgyu rkyen dang 'bras bu'o //
NK063(gu)002:268: ting nge 'dzin las bskyed rim dang /
NK063(gu)002:269: sngags rgya yang shugs la gnas te de dag ston /
NK063(gu)002:270: tha ma'i khyad par ba spyi don sdud pa ma yin pa drug char gyis so //
NK063(gu)002:271: 'di'i le'u'i ngo bo ni mthar lam pa'i yin la shugs las phyag rgya spros pa'i yul lo //
NK063(gu)002:272: bcu drug pa khro bo lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor gyi le'u la /
NK063(gu)002:273: rab kyi lam kho na ste /
NK063(gu)002:274: de las khyad par gyi grol lam rim gyis pa'o //
NK063(gu)002:275: 'bring gi cha rkyen ni dkyil 'khor las khro bo
NK063(gu)002:276: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gsung gi dkyil 'khor ro
NK063(gu)002:277: // ting nge 'dzin las bskyed rim mo //
NK063(gu)002:278: sngags rgya las khro bo'i sngags so //
NK063(gu)002:279: tha ma'i khyad par ba bsnol mtshams 'phen sdud zur tsam mo //
NK063(gu)002:280: 'di yang spros bcas kyi yul lo //
NK063(gu)002:281: bcu bdun pa khro bo lhag pa ting nge 'dzin sku dang thugs kyi le'u la /
NK063(gu)002:282: rab kyi gong ma dang tshul 'dra /
NK063(gu)002:283: 'bring gi cha rkyen ni dkyil 'khor las khro bo lhag pa sku da nga thugs so //
NK063(gu)002:284: ting nge 'dzin las bskyed pa de la khyab pa sngags rgya rnams ston /
NK063(gu)002:285: tha ma'i khyad par ba tshad ma bka' gzhung shas che 'phen sdud zur tsam mo //
NK063(gu)002:286: lam las khyad par ba thabs grol gnyis char ro //
NK063(gu)002:287: bco brgyad pa mchod sbyin dam pa bstan pa'i le'u la /
NK063(gu)002:288: rab kyi ngo bo'i gzhi zur tsam lam kho na ste grol lam rim gyis pa'o //
NK063(gu)002:290: 'bras bu grub pa por mngon tsam mo //
NK063(gu)002:291: 'bring gi cha rkyen lta ba cung zad dang /
NK063(gu)002:293: rmad du byung ba'i spyod pa zur tsam dang /
NK063(gu)002:294: mchod pa nang dang gsang ba bla na med pa'i mchod pa kho na'o //
NK063(gu)002:295: tha ma'i khyad par ba rang bzhin lta ba zur tsam dang ldem dgongs shas che /
NK063(gu)002:296: tshad ma bka' gzhung dang gtar ga zur tsam mo //
NK063(gu)002:297: 'di ni dngos su tshogs sgrub kyi yul lo //
NK063(gu)002:298: bcu dgu pa dam tshig gi le'u la /
NK063(gu)002:301: lam las 'di dam tshig tu 'og ma'i bsrung bya
NK063(gu)002:302: 'dus pa'i phyir thun mong gi lam shugs la ston
NK063(gu)002:303: cing / dngos su khyad par gyi lam grol lam
NK063(gu)002:304: rim gyis pa shas che la cig car ba zur
NK063(gu)002:305: cing / tsam mo // thabs lam nyon mongs pa
NK063(gu)002:306: mi spong zhing bdud rtsi lnga dang du blang ba
NK063(gu)002:307: cing / tsam mo // ston / 'bras bu bdag don grub pa'o //
NK063(gu)002:308: 'bring gi cha rkyen ni dngos dam tshig yin la shugs la lta ba ston /
NK063(gu)002:309: tha ma'i khyad par ba spyi don sdud pa dang mtshon pa dpe ma yin pa lnga yis 'chad /
NK063(gu)002:311: nyi shu pa phrin las kyi le'u la /
NK063(gu)002:312: rab kyi lam kho na ste /
NK063(gu)002:313: gro lam rim gyis pa yin la /
NK063(gu)002:314: thabs lam 'og sgo zur tsam mo //
NK063(gu)002:315: 'bring gi cha rkyen las phrin las te zhi rgyas dbang drag bzhi char ro //
NK063(gu)002:316: de dag las khyab byed du dgos pa don gyi sems ni shugs kyi lta ba'o //
NK063(gu)002:317: tha ma'i khyad par ba bsnol mtshams 'phen sdud dang
NK063(gu)002:318: mtshon pa dpe shas che ldem dgongs zur tsam mo
NK063(gu)002:319: // 'di ni dngos spros bcas yan chad la shugs la kun gyi'o //
NK063(gu)002:320: nyer gcig pa khro bo'i dkyil 'khor la bstod pa'i le'u la /
NK063(gu)002:322: 'bring gi cha rkyen bstod pa'i mchod par rung /
NK063(gu)002:323: tha ma'i khyad par ba mtshon pa dape'o //
NK063(gu)002:324: 'di lam pa bcu bzhi pa dang mtshungs so //
NK063(gu)002:325: tha ma bstan pa gdams shing gtad pa'i le'u la /
NK063(gu)002:327: gzhi las ngo bo'i dang btags pa'i gzhi gnyis char ro //
NK063(gu)002:328: 'bras bu las gzhan don mdzad pa'o //
NK063(gu)002:330: cha rkyen ngos gzung bar mi 'thad /
NK063(gu)002:331: tha ma'i tshad ma bka' gzhung zur tsam gyis 'chad /
NK063(gu)002:332: 'di ni gang zag chos mig can la gtad pa yod phyir kun gyi yul lo //
NK063(gu)002:333: chos tshoms ngos gzung ba zhes bya ba dpal sman
NK063(gu)002:334: lung du mi bskyod rdo rjes nye bar bkod pa'o
